data.description: Welcome to this charming property nestled in the sought-after Stafford Community. This wonderful 3-bedroom, 2.1-bathroom 2-story contemporary home offers an inviting atmosphere from the moment you arrive. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by the home's great curb appeal, highlighted by an oversized and extended concrete driveway. The open-concept layout enhances the sense of space, featuring high ceilings adorned with modern ceiling fans and newly installed lights, complemented by tasteful paint choices throughout. The heart of the home, the eat-in kitchen, is equipped with a flat-top stove and seamlessly flows into the main level laundry area and a full-sized 1-car garage for added convenience. A main level bedroom serves as a versatile bonus space, ideal for guests or as a home office.  Upstairs, you'll find two additional well-appointed bedrooms and two full bathrooms, ensuring comfort and functionality for all occupants. Step outside onto the oversized deck, perfect for entertaining or simply enjoying the serene surroundings of the expansive yard, complete with a lush garden area. For additional storage needs, the full unfinished basement provides ample space, offering versatility to suit your specific requirements. Updated features include an electric heat pump installed in 2008 and a recently replaced architectural shingled roof, ensuring both efficiency and durability. With its move-in ready condition and immediate availability, this premium lot home, presents an excellent opportunity in the desirable Stafford Community . Don't miss out on the chance to make this property your own and schedule your viewing today!
